                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><sub><strong>&#171;</strong> <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/aiad-homescreen">HUB</a> | <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/alert-lockdown-initiated">Part I</a> | <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/command-query-separation">Part II</a> | <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/superencipherment">Part III</a> | <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/clock-multiplier">Part IV</a> | <span style="color: blue">Part V: Null-terminating String</span> <strong>&#187;</strong></sub></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div style="text-align: right;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">rating:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+243</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="I like it" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="I don't like it" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="Cancel my vote" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>



<p><br />
<br /></p>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #c0504d; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#ca612c; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#c6615e), to(#c0504d)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#c6615e, #ca612c); background:-o-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #c0504d); background:linear-gradient(#c6615e, #c0504d); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>So that's your official opinion?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float: right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#fff0f0; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#8b8b8b), to(#7F7F7F)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#8b8b8b, #656565); background:-o-linear-gradient(#8b8b8b, #7F7F7F); background:linear-gradient(#8b8b8b, #7F7F7F); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>So far, yes. Though we aren't ruling out sabotage&#8230; pending investigation, of course.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #c0504d; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#ca612c; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#c6615e), to(#c0504d)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#c6615e, #ca612c); background:-o-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #c0504d); background:linear-gradient(#c6615e, #c0504d); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>Alright then. That's what I'll tell the director. He's under the impression that servers don't just burn up for no reason. Frankly, I'm inclined to agree with him.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float: right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#fff0f0; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#8b8b8b), to(#7F7F7F)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#8b8b8b, #656565); background:-o-linear-gradient(#8b8b8b, #7F7F7F); background:linear-gradient(#8b8b8b, #7F7F7F); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>Har har. The thing is that with the lockdown, nothing was getting in or out. So even if there were logs of the event, they'd be lost with the other files.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #c0504d; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#ca612c; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#c6615e), to(#c0504d)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#c6615e, #ca612c); background:-o-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #c0504d); background:linear-gradient(#c6615e, #c0504d); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>So we'll never know what caused it?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float: right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#fff0f0; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#8b8b8b), to(#7F7F7F)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#8b8b8b, #656565); background:-o-linear-gradient(#8b8b8b, #7F7F7F); background:linear-gradient(#8b8b8b, #7F7F7F); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>You're welcome to rummage through what didn't get melted into slag.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #c0504d; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#ca612c; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#c6615e), to(#c0504d)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#c6615e, #ca612c); background:-o-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #c0504d); background:linear-gradient(#c6615e, #c0504d); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>Pass. I think everyone is just relieved that the incident was restricted to the server room. Nothing that can't be restored from the off-site backups.</p>
<p>What about Glacon?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 30px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float: right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#fff0f0; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#8b8b8b), to(#7F7F7F)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#8b8b8b, #656565); background:-o-linear-gradient(#8b8b8b, #7F7F7F); background:linear-gradient(#8b8b8b, #7F7F7F); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>He was getting decommed anyway.</p>
<p>Alexandra is currently allocating space for 17 on the 19 servers. Setting up temporary symbolic links and all that. Just until the hardware is replaced.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #c0504d; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#ca612c; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#c6615e), to(#c0504d)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#c6615e, #ca612c); background:-o-linear-gradient(#d9682f, #c0504d); background:linear-gradient(#c6615e, #c0504d); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>Good. AIAD is looking good right now, helping 17 with the quick recovery. I wouldn't be surprised if some of those recent budget requests come through.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/bozkurt2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="bozkurt2.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float: right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #7F7F7F; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-border-radius:30px /70px; -moz-border-radius:30px /70px; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#fff0f0; background:-webkit-gradient(linear, 0 0, 0 100%, from(#8b8b8b), to(#7F7F7F)); background:-moz-linear-gradient(#8b8b8b, #656565); background:-o-linear-gradient(#8b8b8b, #7F7F7F); background:linear-gradient(#8b8b8b, #7F7F7F); text-align: left; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px;">
<p>Yup. And it's all going straight into your department's Gen5 development.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/null-terminating-string/lurk2.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="lurk2.png" class="image" /></div>
